ca.ualberta.ridr

Class Request

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.ridr.Request

  • public class Request
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a request object, which is when a Rider makes a request for somebody to drive them somewhere. This gets turned into a ride object when the Rider chooses a driver to fulfill their request.
